- Keep the property adequately heated and ventilated to prevent condensation, dampness and mould
- Report any defects or damage to the Landlord without unreasonable delay
- Not cause damage to the property (fair wear and tear excepted)
- Make good any damage caused by the Tenant, members of the Tenant's household, or visitors

